---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-12 py-24">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold mb-5 text-gray-900">>_ Hai, gue Zul. 👋</h1>
      <p class="text-2xl text-gray-400 italic mb-12">
        Professional Procrastinator who somehow builds data things.
      </p>
      <div class="text-xl leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl">
        <p>
          💼 Udah nyentuh banyak hal di dunia kerja — finance, IT, data ops.
          Masih penasaran sama banyak hal lainnya.
        </p>
        <p>
          🖥️ Punya homelab sendiri, lagi bangun sesuatu yang beneran kepake.
        </p>
        <p>
          ✏️ Nulis di sini buat diri sendiri sebenernya. Semacam catatan harian
          yang dipublish — soal data, teknis, random, dan kadang terlalu jujur.
        </p>
        <p>Kalau lo nyasar ke sini, enjoy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <a
          href="/blog"
          class="text-base text-gray-900 underline hover:text-gray-500 transition-colors"
          >Baca tulisan →</a
        >
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
